<p>Lebanon released Hannibal Gaddafi on Monday after he paid US$900,000 bail, ending almost ten years of pre-trial detention in a probe linked to the disappearance of Lebanese Shia cleric Musa al‑Sadr. His lawyer said the 49‑year‑old is officially free and may leave Lebanon once formal paperwork is completed, according to defence team statements and reporting. Authorities allege he withheld information about Musa al‑Sadr&#x27;s disappearance but he was never tried during his years in custody.</p><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Defence comments: Hannibal’s lawyer, Charbel Milad al‑Khoury, told reporters the release followed completion of necessary paperwork by the defence team.</li><li>Case origin: The central investigation concerns the 1978 disappearance of Musa al‑Sadr, a Lebanese Shia cleric last seen during a visit to Libya in 1978.</li><li>Family background: Hannibal is identified in reports as the youngest son of former Libyan leader Muammar Gaddafi and is reported to be 49 years old.</li><li>Official confirmation: Two Lebanese security officials confirmed to journalists that his release followed bail payment and completion of legal formalities.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Hannibal Gaddafi&#x27;s defence: The defence team said he is officially free and can leave Lebanon after paperwork was completed. (<a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/middle-east/article/3332293/gaddafis-son-released-bail-after-10-years-lebanon-prison'>SCMP</a>)</li><li>Lebanese security officials: Security officials told reporters the release followed payment of bail and completion of formalities. (<a href='https://www.arabnews.com/node/2622130/middle-east'>Arab News</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.rt.com/africa/627612-lebanon-releases-gaddafis-son/'>Lebanon releases Gaddafi’s son</a> - rt.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/middle-east/article/3332293/gaddafis-son-released-bail-after-10-years-lebanon-prison'>Gaddafi’s son released on bail after 10 years in a Lebanon prison</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/comments/1otxzdj/hannibal_gadhafi_son_of_late_libyan_leader/'>Hannibal Gadhafi, son of late Libyan leader Moammar, released by Lebanon after 10 years in detention</a> - reddit.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/czxnq6d71y9o'>Gaddafi&#x27;s youngest son released after 10 years in Lebanese detention</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.rfi.fr/en/international/20251111-lebanon-frees-frees-hannibal-kadhafi-son-of-libya-s-ex-leader-held-for-a-decade'>Lebanon frees frees Hannibal Kadhafi, son of Libya’s ex-leader, held for a decade</a> - rfi.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.arabnews.com/node/2622130/middle-east'>Lebanon grants a US$900,000 bail to Hannibal Gaddafi, the son of former Libyan leader Muammar Gaddafi, ending his nearly 10-year detention in a case involving the 1978 disappearance of Shia Muslim cleric Musa al-Sadr, for which Gaddafi was accused of withholding information but never tried.</a> - arabnews.com</li></ul>